[Name] Tolua++
[Summary] Extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code with Lua. 
[Description] tolua++ is an extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code with Lua.
tolua++ includes new features oriented to c++ such as support for std::string as a basic type
(this can be turned off by a command line option) and support for class templates,
as well as other features and bugfixes. 
[License] MIT/X11
[Homepage] http://www.codenix.com/~tolua/

